{"tid":972284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【智慧老人】華人作家III 李怡特輯 (港台電視31製作；《地厚天高》林子穎編導)","createTime":"2019-01-07T09:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T13:39:50.000Z","uid":35221,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad1dd0285a7e7191ab3ef79784a004270b0b9ef1","tid":972284,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:37:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CxnSVqSJYo4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCxnSVqSJYo4&d=MmsljSwmbRLmMNnuRoW8HwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e4e07859\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CxnSVqSJYo4</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《坐看雲起時》- 李怡<br />\n<br />\n李怡先生為人所熟知的是他的政論文章，和他曾是「七十年代」、「九十年代」雜誌創刊人，他的文章以對時勢的批判性和辛辣見稱，但或許讀者不知道李怡最初是寫情書開始他的作家生涯，原來他有其柔情的一面。<br />\n<br />\n《坐看雲起時》介紹這位政論名筆在寫作方面的貢獻，追索他如何由擁護共產主義的文化青年，演變成晚年狠批中共政權的文壇旗手之心路歷程。我們更會漫步於李怡先生的感情世界，由於早年他與愛妻天各一方，我們可閱讀到當年他寫給妻子的情信、情詩，和感動於他歷年不懈對亡妻的思念。<br />\n<br />\n編導:林子穎（電影《地厚天高》導演 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"0f9a712b45a911c2ef1fdbf55e25cf2eaa8263d6","tid":972284,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:40:22.000Z","msg":"片中有堂主、游氏片段"},{"pid":"b99c86447d286f600614646a287a39e74e7811b4","tid":972284,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8563ab0fda9185a62d5340e2eefcf9075af53e03","tid":972284,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f9a712b45a911c2ef1fdbf55e25cf2eaa8263d6","tid":972284,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:40:22.000Z","msg":"片中有堂主、游氏片段"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:50:28.000Z","msg":"重有練老乙錚"},{"pid":"d1e6f1559af3504bebad7816be25e03